<a-band full>
    <div slot="header">
        <h2 class="title">Why choose Allons-y Consulting?</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p class="header-summary">Allons-y (<em>ah-lo(n)-zee</em>) is an idiomatic French expression meaning roughly, <strong>"Let's go!"</strong> That's exactly the energy we bring to design systems and digital transformation work.</p>
        <p><strong class="extra">We help organizations build front-end infrastructure that scales and manage complex technical initiatives that drive business outcomes.</strong></p>
        <p class="header-summary">Founded in 2025, we combine deep technical expertise in design systems and web standards with proven program management capabilities. Whether you need someone to architect your component library, lead a multi-million dollar digital transformation, or bridge the gap between design, engineering, and business strategy—we deliver results.</p>
        <p class="header-summary">We believe the best technology is invisible&emdash;it empowers teams to do their best work without getting in the way. We specialize in creating infrastructure, establishing workflows, and leading initiatives that make complex problems feel manageable.</p>
    </div>
</a-band>
